/www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles\n/PMC7666174/bin/41467_2020_19585_MOESM7_ESM.txt\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\">Supplementary Data 4</a><sup>(42K, txt)</sup></span></span><span class=\"sec suppmat\" id=\"MOESM8\"><span class=\"sup-box half_rhythm\" id=\"idm139884796560416\"><a target=\"_BLANK\" href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles\n/PMC7666174/bin/41467_2020_19585_MOESM8_ESM.xlsx\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\">Supplementary Data 5</a><sup>(63K, xlsx)</sup></span></span><span class=\"sec suppmat\" id=\"MOESM9\"><span class=\"sup-box half_rhythm\" id=\"idm139884796557536\"><a target=\"_BLANK\" href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles\n/PMC7666174/bin/41467_2020_19585_MOESM9_ESM.xlsx\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\">Supplementary Data 6</a><sup>(535K, xlsx)</sup></span></span><span class=\"sec suppmat\" id=\"MOESM10\"><span class=\"sup-box half_rhythm\" id=\"idm139884796554656\"><a target=\"_BLANK\" href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles\n/PMC7666174/bin/41467_2020_19585_MOESM10_ESM.xlsx\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\">Supplementary Data 7</a><sup>(16K, xlsx)</sup></span></span><span class=\"sec suppmat\" id=\"MOESM11\"><span class=\"sup-box half_rhythm\" id=\"idm139884797129856\"><a target=\"_BLANK\" href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles\n/PMC7666174/bin/41467_2020_19585_MOESM11_ESM.xlsx\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\">Supplementary Data 8</a><sup>(36K, xlsx)</sup></span></span><span class=\"sec suppmat\" id=\"MOESM12\"><span class=\"sup-box half_rhythm\" id=\"idm139884797126976\"><a target=\"_BLANK\" href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles\n/PMC7666174/bin/41467_2020_19585_MOESM12_ESM.xlsx\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\">Supplementary Data 9</a><sup>(39K, xlsx)</sup></span></span><span class=\"sec suppmat\" id=\"MOESM13\"><span class=\"sup-box half_rhythm\" id=\"idm139884797124096\"><a target=\"_BLANK\" href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles\n/PMC7666174/bin/41467_2020