+Zhao&amp;author=F+Zhang&amp;author=X+Ding&amp;author=G+Wu&amp;author=YY+Lam&amp;volume=359&amp;publication_year=2018&amp;pages=1151-1156&amp;pmid=29590046&amp;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" ref=\"reftype=other&amp;article-id=6760872&amp;issue-id=342668&amp;journal-id=319&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar\">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li></ul></div></div><br>', NULL, 1);
