eum versus colon, ASP250-altered gut microbiota</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">15&#x000a0;wks</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">United States</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/bioproject/PRJNA72355\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\" ref=\"reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=5443231&amp;issue-id=292354&amp;journal-id=3105&amp;FROM=Article%7CBody&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI\" target=\"_blank\">PRJNA72355</a></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><a href=\"#B8\" rid=\"B8\" class=\" bibr popnode\">8</a></td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">101</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">V1 to V3</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">454 FLX</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">54.1%</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">PowerSoil DNA isolation kit</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">Fecal</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">Carbadox resulted in early but not late alterations of the fecal microbiota</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">6&#x02013;15&#x000a0;wks</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">United States</td><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/bioproject/237795\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\" ref=\"reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=5443231&amp;issue-id=292354&amp;journal-id=3105&amp;FROM=Article%7CBody&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI\" target=\"_blank\">PRJNA237795</a>; <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/biosample/SAMN02645017\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\" ref=\"reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=5443231&amp;issue-id=292354&amp;journal-id=3105&amp;FROM=Article%7CBody&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI\" target=\"_blank\">SAMN02645017</a> to <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/biosample/SAMN02645066\" data-ga-action=\"click_feat_suppl\" ref=\"reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=5443231&amp;issue-id=292354&amp;journal-id=3105&amp;FROM=Article%7CBody&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI\" target=\"_blank\">SAMN02645066</a></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><a href=\"#B69\" rid=\"B69\" class=\"